strings:
<voice_0x010012E8><se_low>Marta: Go north from the bottom of the mountain
and you will come to Orkutsk.
Please be careful on your journey.

<voice_0x010012EA><se_low>King Trode: Princess! Are you all right?
Were you cold in the night!?
<voice_0x010012EB><se_low>Marta: Forgive me, but I must ask you a favour.
<voice_0x010012EC><se_low>Marta: If you meet with a man called Marek in Orkutsk, please give this to him.

<voice_0x010012ED><se_low>Marta: He is probably working with herbs like I am.
I would be grateful if you could give him that bag. Spasibo! Thank you.
<voice_0x010012EE><se_low>King Trode: Right then. Off to Orkutsk! Toodlee-bye!
